name: Samurai Dude-Hizaru 氷猿-PE
description:
He is agile in the sword, reliable in combat tactics, not easily frightened when in front like a solid wall that protect the castle from attack, born in winter to grow into a respected figure amongst warriors the name is Hizaru or The Winter Monkey.

The prime editions of Samurai Dude-Hizaru 氷猿
